<h1>Psychological triggers</h1>

<div class="columns">

<div class="column">
<p>We've looked at making sure the content of your page is arranged in a way to attract your visitor's eye to the most important element, but there are other ways you can persuade them to take the action you want. These are known as psychological and emotional triggers.</p>
</div>
    
